name: A Journey Through Life by Lola

metadata.name: Trees and Petals
metadata.description:
Trees and Petals

Nature is all around us as well as deep within us. We are closely linked to nature; our bodies, lives, and thoughts rely on the air we breathe and the food we eat. 

''I painted this during my school year. My teacher told me to paint something I am inspired by, and that day I was thinking of trees and nature'' 

1/1 Special Edition
